Package: aces
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Constrained Enveloping Splines
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
  person(
    given = "Víctor J.", 
    family = "España", 
    email = "vespana@umh.es",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1807-6180"))
Description: Estimates maximum attainable outputs with adaptive regression
    splines and uses them to construct production technologies. The package
    provides Adaptive Constrained Enveloping Splines (ACES), Random Forest ACES
    (RF-ACES), and a faster Quick ACES variant. It also computes radial,
    directional, Russell, and weighted additive efficiency measures and their
    efficient targets.
